274
00:15:15,894 --> 00:15:17,594
A stupid trick!

275
00:15:17,594 --> 00:15:22,594
But the cloth that fell... Wouldn't it be found by someone?

276
00:15:22,594 --> 00:15:23,894
Masumi.

277
00:15:23,894 --> 00:15:25,194
Masumi?

278
00:15:25,194 --> 00:15:27,794
I don't think you saw,

279
00:15:27,794 --> 00:15:31,594
