283
00:15:41,794 --> 00:15:45,794
If you keep holding the button of the switch down

284
00:15:45,794 --> 00:15:47,394
and attach it to the weight that is suspending

285
00:15:47,394 --> 00:15:49,094
from the railing of the veranda...

286
00:15:57,194 --> 00:16:00,894
Simultaneous to the cloth falling, the roof of the car closes.

287
00:16:00,894 --> 00:16:04,594
Just the car that is parked in a strange place is left behind!

288
00:16:05,394 --> 00:16:08,094
By the way, this trick does not work

289
00:16:08,094 --> 00:16:10,494
unless he gets me into this room at 9:00 sharp

290
00:16:10,494 --> 00:16:14,294
when the construction stars.

291
00:16:14,294 --> 00:16:19,494
That's why the perp set his cell phone to ring a minute before 9:00.

292
00:16:20,194 --> 00:16:22,294
Wait!

293
00:16:22,294 --> 00:16:24,194
An incoming call.

294
00:16:24,194 --> 00:16:26,094
Hello, Mr. Hotta?

295
00:16:26,094 --> 00:16:28,194
Are you Mr. Hotta?

296
00:16:28,194 --> 00:16:31,494
I'm sorry. It was a wrong number.

297
00:16:31,494 --> 00:16:33,294
By doing so,

298
00:16:33,294 --> 00:16:35,394
the timing in which the bellboy uses the key

299
00:16:35,394 --> 00:16:38,594
to open the door can be controlled.

300
00:16:38,594 --> 00:16:43,594
If the e-mail asking for help was sent by the victim an hour earlier,

301
00:16:43,594 --> 00:16:46,494
the victim was probably killed at that time, too.

302
00:16:46,494 --> 00:16:48,594
In this country where earthquakes are frequent,

303
00:16:48,594 --> 00:16:53,694
it'll not be reasonable to keep the salt trick as if for many hours.

304
00:16:53,694 --> 00:16:58,094
If so, it should still be in his car,

305
00:16:58,094 --> 00:17:00,694
the heavy weight and cloth that he used for the truck, of course,

306
00:17:00,694 --> 00:17:04,294
as well as the murder weapon he used to kill Hotta

307
00:17:04,294 --> 00:17:06,694
and clothing splattered with blood.

308
00:17:08,594 --> 00:17:10,594
Yes.

309
00:17:10,594 --> 00:17:14,894
The blood splattered clothes are still in the trunk of the car.

310
00:17:16,194 --> 00:17:19,794
Together with the knife I used to punish that guy

311
00:17:19,794 --> 00:17:22,694
who dared to expose my younger sister's corpse to public view.

312
00:17:22,694 --> 00:17:24,994
Your younger sister's corpse?

313
00:17:24,994 --> 00:17:26,594
Several years ago,

314
00:17:26,594 --> 00:17:29,594
my younger sister killed herself on a certain mountain.

315
00:17:29,594 --> 00:17:32,494
A death note saying that she hung herself

316
00:17:32,494 --> 00:17:35,294
after going through the shock of a heartbreak.

317
00:17:35,294 --> 00:17:39,094
But no matter how hard I looked, I couldn't find her corpse.

318
00:17:39,094 --> 00:17:40,594
And yet!

319
00:17:40,594 --> 00:17:42,494
On a TV program,

320
00:17:42,494 --> 00:17:44,494
Gaito Hotta declared that on a certain mountain

321
00:17:44,494 --> 00:17:49,094
he smelled death of a different person from the one he was searching for

322
00:17:49,094 --> 00:17:50,894
and discovered the corpse of my younger sister

323
00:17:50,894 --> 00:17:53,094
that was buried under the soil.

324
00:17:53,094 --> 00:17:55,194
Do you see what I'm getting at?

325
00:17:55,194 --> 00:17:59,294
Despite having found my younger sister who hung herself,

326
00:17:59,294 --> 00:18:01,094
that guy buried her in the soil

327
00:18:01,094 --> 00:18:03,694
without even reporting to the police!

328
00:18:03,694 --> 00:18:04,794
He put on this performance

329
00:18:04,794 --> 00:18:07,694
just to show what spiritual powers he possessed!

330
00:18:07,694 --> 00:18:11,694
That's why I...

331
00:18:16,094 --> 00:18:18,294
Gosh!

332
00:18:18,294 --> 00:18:20,494
She went back to the room next door.

333
00:18:21,994 --> 00:18:24,494
Okay. Let's hear the rest of what you have to say at the station.

334
00:18:24,494 --> 00:18:26,794
Not yet.

335
00:18:26,794 --> 00:18:28,594
I've got to tell her.

336
00:18:28,594 --> 00:18:30,494
I've got to go report to my sister's grave

337
00:18:30,494 --> 00:18:34,994
that I punished the man who put her death to shame.

338
00:18:35,894 --> 00:18:37,394
Hey!

339
00:18:41,094 --> 00:18:42,494
Hey!

340
00:18:43,494 --> 00:18:45,394
Crap! In the next room, there's...

341
00:18:48,394 --> 00:18:50,594
Who are you?

342
00:18:57,194 --> 00:18:58,394
Gosh!

343
00:18:58,394 --> 00:18:59,794
Move out of my way!

344
00:19:05,094 --> 00:19:06,994
Is he dead?

345
00:19:08,794 --> 00:19:13,494
No. She accurately hit his vitals and struck him out cold.

346
00:19:13,494 --> 00:19:16,694
In the few seconds that it took me to get here

347
00:19:16,694 --> 00:19:20,194
with the speed comparable to that of the secret service...

348
00:19:20,194 --> 00:19:23,294
The one who did this is... is without doubt...

349
00:19:23,294 --> 00:19:24,894
The untouchable...

350
00:19:24,894 --> 00:19:26,294
Mom!

351
00:19:27,594 --> 00:19:31,394
No. Are you okay, Conan?

352
00:19:31,394 --> 00:19:32,994
Yeah.

353
00:19:32,994 --> 00:19:35,394
Mom?

354
00:19:39,194 --> 00:19:42,494
Well, it's you all right, Mom.

355
00:19:42,494 --> 00:19:47,694
To be able to use Conan's bowtie device right on the spot!

356
00:19:47,694 --> 00:19:52,194
Yeah. There was a mark on the dial, you see.

357
00:19:52,194 --> 00:19:55,994
He was probably using the voice of that detective a lot.

358
00:19:55,994 --> 00:19:57,694
How amazing though...

359
00:19:57,694 --> 00:20:00,394
