361
00:20:02,994 --> 00:20:06,394
I was able to imagine using it in a variety of situations.

362
00:20:06,394 --> 00:20:08,394
It's so exciting.

363
00:20:10,794 --> 00:20:12,994
I guess so.

364
00:20:12,994 --> 00:20:15,494
You don't look all that excited, though.

365
00:20:15,494 --> 00:20:16,794
And?

366
00:20:16,794 --> 00:20:20,694
Did you find out what information Hotta got a hold of?

367
00:20:20,694 --> 00:20:21,694
Yeah.

368
00:20:21,694 --> 00:20:25,294
Just before being taken to the polite man called Kokuri was saying

369
00:20:25,294 --> 00:20:28,594
