371
00:20:31,894 --> 00:20:35,994
It seems that Hotta found out that Asaka was a woman.

372
00:20:35,994 --> 00:20:38,594
He was going to summon the spirit of Koji Haneda

373
00:20:38,594 --> 00:20:44,394
