374
00:20:44,394 --> 00:20:47,194
So, that's it? Trash!

375
00:20:47,194 --> 00:20:49,294
More importantly, start packing.

376
00:20:49,294 --> 00:20:50,694
We're moving out.

377
00:20:50,694 --> 00:20:52,094
What? Already?

378
00:20:52,094 --> 00:20:53,294
I was thinking how lucky I was

379
00:20:53,294 --> 00:20:56,394
