380
00:20:58,394 --> 00:21:01,594
No one knows Conan's true identity.

381
00:21:01,594 --> 00:21:04,194
Always keep on your guard when around Conan Edogawa.

382
00:21:04,194 --> 00:21:09,894
He's a totally different person from the boy we met 10 years ago.

383
00:21:09,894 --> 00:21:11,394
Okay.

