Asaka's a bodyguard and a woman.

385
00:22:36,994 --> 00:22:41,494
If that person is the number 2 of the Black Organization, Rum...

386
00:22:41,494 --> 00:22:45,094
Then maybe the one that Ai referred to as an effeminate man

387
