397
00:23:24,994 --> 00:23:29,694
I could care less about the job that Rum goofed on 17 years ago.

398
00:23:29,694 --> 00:23:33,294
What bothers me more is the Sleeping Kogoro.

399
00:23:34,194 --> 00:23:39,294
It seems that he was involved in solving that case this morning, too.

400
00:23:40,194 --> 00:23:43,394
It's not clear what his true identity is

